title: Educator WordPress
description:
Duration 8 hours 43 minutes

Jim Hague helps you utilize WordPress to create spectacular websites without having to worry about coding. Jim has over 15+ years experience designing websites, developing media products, and creating dozens of WordPress sites. He covers both WordPress.com (free hosting) and WordPress.org (self hosting) and helps you choose and set up the best option. Jim teaches through tons of real world examples and makes technical jargon easy to understand. He goes over everything from setup, uploading media, editing themes, SEO, and widgets to syndicating and backing up your blog.
